{"tid":2113782,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"interview表現預測有冇offer","createTime":"2020-07-18T10:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T17:23:00.000Z","uid":152224,"like":18,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"73037f7a9cf9a8109f335dd0e816abe18002af18","tid":2113782,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"根據小弟in過20份工嘅經驗<br />\n發現到以下嘅現象<br />\n<br />\n冇offer:<br />\n1. individual interview 時間短 (5-10mins) / dead air<br />\n2. 問你幾句個人背景就講：仲有冇其他問題想問? / 有消息會今個星期內通知你 / 要考慮下先，仲會in其他candidate   <br />\n3. 考官黑面/冇笑容<br />\n4. 唔著suit (視乎工種) / 冇盪衫 / 衫有污漬 <br />\n5. 冇拎你帶黎嘅文件副本<br />\n<span class=\"red\">6. in完後自我感覺良好</span><br />\n <br />\n有offer:<br />\n1. individual interview 時間長 (&gt;15mins)<br />\n2. 問到好深入 / 好free咁傾計  (e.g. 家人、興趣、學習)<br />\n3. 考官有笑容<br />\n4. 著suit (視乎工種) / 有盪衫 / 乾淨 <br />\n5. 問你最快幾時返到工 / 聯絡方法 / nickname<br />\n<span class=\"red\">6. in完後覺得玩撚完 </span>"},{"pid":"78a5477ce50998cbb91c778a1ee296f27d50e428","tid":2113782,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"Lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cea9dd94e38be097e72e5f574a09ea1f91b0924","tid":2113782,"uid":104804,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"20份都未有OFFER?"},{"pid":"1d120cdee3c4733ec9c12e020acde2c087f2bcbf","tid":2113782,"uid":185092,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"第6點講得好中"},{"pid":"c24539b842b56bade73102c72ebf5ce5e26ab3d6","tid":2113782,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n仲要第六點準到仆街"},{"pid":"b135b1c2a73f6b733fc8eb6719c0c8a4de93dd58","tid":2113782,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"最準第6點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e61875b9327291031dc04b194ec3d78